      "bezeichnung": "Pressure Sensor Node",
      "kreditpunkte": 0,
      "lernziele": "<ul>\n<li style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">Professional expertise: the student<br />- can solve a technical problem in the field of embedded systems<br />- has profound knowledge in microcontroller programming running an RTOS</li>\n<li style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">Methodical expertise: The student<br />- demonstrates his capability for analysis, creativity, logical thinking.</li>\n<li style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">Social competence:<br />- Communicative and cooperation skills</li>\n<li style=\"background-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; color: #000000; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\">Self-competence:<br />- Autonomy, responsibility</li>\n</ul>",
      "planinhalt": "<ul>\n<li>Study and understanding of the system architecture (e.g. CAN FD bus)</li>\n<li>Development of Firmware for the Pressure sensor node<br />- Enable data collection of pressure signal and pre-processing of the signal (e.g. filtering) by Pressure sensor node<br />- Establish communication between Gateway and Pressure sensor node (plug and play)<br />- Implement Pelion Device Management to do FW Upload, Configuration Update over CAN-FD</li>\n<li>Verification phase to ensure that data is correctly send and received</li>\n<li>Present the achieved result and final report.</li>\n</ul>",
